r-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">of organizations using AI (up from 78% in 2024)</td></tr><tr class="border-b border-border"><td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px 12px 1px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 1px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Large Enterprise Adoption</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-right" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 14px; text-align: right; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="font-semibold text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: right; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">79%</span></td><td class="py-3 pl-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 1px 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 1px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16