b(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Tier 1</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Advanced implementation (RAG, agents, fine-tuning)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Multi-model strategy, governance, LLMOps</td><td class="py-3 pl-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 1px 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 1px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="font-semibold" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Gap:</span> Advanced technical content needed</td></tr><tr class="border-b border-border bg-llpa-blue/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px 12px 1px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 1px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Tier 2</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Role-based AI applications, pilot-to-production</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Change management, ROI measurement</td><td class="py-3 pl-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 1px 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 1px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="font-semibold" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Partial:</span> Role-based content exists</td></tr><tr class="border-b border-border bg-llpa-yellow/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px 12px 1px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 1px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Tier 3</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Foundational GenAI, prompt engineering basics</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Use case discovery, executive awareness</td><td class="py-3 pl-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 1px 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 1px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="font-semibold" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Strong:</span> Core curriculum aligned</td></tr><tr class="border-b border-border bg-llpa-orange/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px 12px 1px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 1px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Tier 4</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">AI literacy, digital foundations</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Executive education, infrastructure basics</td><td class="py-3 pl-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 1px 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 1px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="font-semibold" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Strong:</span> Awareness content available</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="mt-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h5 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2 flex items-center gap-2" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-llpa-orange/15 " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(232, 91, 48, 0.15); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-triangle-alert w-3.5 h-3.5 text-llpa-orange"><path d="m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3"></path><path d="M12 9v4"></path><path d="M12 17h.01"></path></svg></div>Strategic Implication</h5><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Organizations in Tier 3-4 markets focus on foundational AI capabilities. Tier 1-2 markets — where enterprises have significant AI budgets and are actively seeking implementation support — represent the highest-value opportunities but require more advanced capabilities to serve effectively.</p></div></div><div id="section-1-1-maturity-methodology" class="mb-6" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 flex items-center gap-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-llpa-green/15 " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(104, 198, 57, 0.15); font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-flask-conical w-3.5 h-3.5 text-llpa-green"><path d="M10 2v7.527a2 2 0 0 1-.211.896L4.72 20.55a1 1 0 0 0 .9 1.45h12.76a1 1 0 0 0 .9-1.45l-5.069-10.127A2 2 0 0 1 14 9.527V2"></path><path d="M8.5 2h7"></path><path d="M7 16h10"></path></svg></div>Methodology</h4><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">This methodology describes how the maturity tier framework was created. It establishes standardized criteria for classifying markets into tiers, enabling consistent comparison of market readiness and AI adoption maturity.</p><div class="mb-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h5 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Four-Factor Assessment</h5><div class="overflow-x-auto" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><table class="w-full text-sm"><thead><tr class="border-b-2 border-foreground"><th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 font-semibold text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px 12px 1px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 1px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Factor</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">What It Measures</th><th class="text-left py-3 pl-4 font-semibold text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 1px 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 1px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Data Source</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="border-b border-border"><td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px 12px 1px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 1px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0p