35); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Microsoft AI Diffusion data positions Croatia among moderate global AI adopters. Investment in AI and cloud infrastructure, digital skills, and regional collaboration will be essential for accelerating adoption.</span><a href="#mp-ref-71" class="text-llpa-blue hover:text-llpa-blue/80 cursor-pointer font-medium text-[10px] align-super" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 10px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[71]</a><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="country-slovenia" class="border border-border rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-card scroll-mt-24" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><div class="p-6 border-b border-border bg-muted/30" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(240, 242, 244, 0.3); font-size: 16px; padding: 24px; padding-top: 24px; padding-right: 24px; padding-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 24px; border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 