x; padding-right: 4px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-left: 4px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 4px;">418</span><div class="min-w-0 flex-1" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p class="font-body text-[11px] font-medium text-foreground truncate" title="AI Agents for Human Work" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 11px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">AI Agents for Human Work</p><p class="font-body text-[10px] text-muted-foreground truncate" title="Benchmarking Agents Against Real-World Work - mapping 43 benchmarks to 1,016 occupations (2026)" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 10px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Benchmarking Agents Against Real-World Work - mapping 43 benchmarks to 1,016 occupations (2026)</p></div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-3 w-3 text-muted-foreground shrink-0 transition-transform"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-4 text-center" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; text-align: center; margin-top: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span>Show Less <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-up h-4 w-4"><path d="m18 15-6-6-6 6"></path></svg></span></div></div></section></div></div></section></div></div></div><div id="section-1-2" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 64px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="mb-12" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-6" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">1.2 Cross-Market Adoption Patterns</h3><div class="mb-8" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class=" mb-8 space-y-4" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="flex items-start gap-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-llpa-green/15 mt-0.5" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(104, 198, 57, 0.15); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 2px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-flask-conical w-3.5 h-3.5 text-llpa-green"><path d="M10 2v7.527a2 2 0 0 1-.211.896L4.72 20.55a1 1 0 0 0 .9 1.45h12.76a1 1 0 0 0 .9-1.45l-5.069-10.127A2 2 0 0 1 14 9.527V2"></path><path d="M8.5 2h7"></path><path d="M7 16h10"></path></svg></div><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed flex-1" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong class="text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Methodology:</strong> Analysis of enterprise AI adoption data across global markets spanning Europe, Asia-Pacific, Americas, Middle East, and Africa. Patterns identified through statistical correlation analysis and market research synthesis from 413 sources.</p></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-llpa-blue/15 mt-0.5" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.15); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 2px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-target w-3.5 h-3.5 text-llpa-blue"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg></div><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed flex-1" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong class="text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Objective:</strong> Identify recurring adoption dynamics that transcend individual markets to understand enterprise AI maturity patterns and value realization challenges.</p></div></div></div><div class="mb-8 p-6 rounded-xl border border-llpa-blue/25 bg-llpa-blue/5" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.05); font-size: 16px; padding: 24px; padding-top: 24px; padding-right: 24px; padding-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px; border: 1px solid rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.25); border-top: 1px solid rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.25); border-right: 1px solid rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.25); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.25); border-left: 1px solid rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.25); border-color: rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.25); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 12px;"><h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center gap-2" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-globe w-5 h-5 text-llpa-blue shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20"></path><path d="M2 12h20"></path></svg>Romania in cross-market context</h4><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Cross-market patterns above apply to Romania as a <strong class="text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Tier 2 (Advanced)</strong> market in our framework: strong IT services and technical talent, but <strong class="text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">enterprise AI adoption is the lowest in the EU and concentrated in large enterprises</strong>. The headline gap looks small because the floor is so low; the size-class divide is actually more pronounced than the EU average.</p><ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground list-disc pl-5"><li style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Eurostat enterprise AI usage: <strong class="text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">5.21%</strong> of Romanian enterprises (2025 data)—lowest in the EU versus the EU average of ~20%; Denmark leads at 42.03% for contrast.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Eurostat December 2025: EU enterprise AI adoption reached 20.0%" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[375]</sup></li><li style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Size-class breakdown: <strong class="text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">large enterprises 20.75%</strong> vs <strong class="text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">small (10–49) 4.13%</strong> — a <strong class="text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">5.0x ratio</strong>, the most concentrated divide in the Pattern 1 table above (EU average is 3.7x). The 17pp absolute gap understates the structural distance between large and small Romanian firms.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Eurostat December 2025: EU enterprise AI adoption reached 20.0%" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[375]</sup></li><li style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Individual use of generative AI tools among citizens was <strong class="text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">17.8%</strong> in 2025—the lowest in the EU, signalling room for literacy and enablement programs.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Eurostat: 32.7% of EU people used generative AI tools in 2025 (December 2025 release)" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[517]</sup></li><li style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Romania sits with Poland (8.4%) and Bulgaria (8.5%) in the lower band of EU adoption; the IT outsourcing sector creates a bridge to scale delivery once enterprise demand accelerates among small and mid-market firms.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Eurostat December 2025: EU enterprise AI adoption reached 20.0%" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[375]</sup></li></ul><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-4" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">For event collateral and country-specific talking points, see the full <a class="text-llpa-blue font-medium hover:underline" href="/market-profiles" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Romania market profile</a>.</p></div><div id="pattern-1" class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6 border border-border shadow-sm mb-10" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; padding: 24px; padding-top: 24px; padding-right: 24px; padding-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 40px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 12px;"><h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center gap-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-llpa-green/15 " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(104, 198, 57, 0.15); font-weight: 600; font-size: 20px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-building2 w-4 h-4 text-llpa-green"><path d="M6 22V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v18Z"></path><path d="M6 12H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2"></path><path d="M18 9h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2"></path><path d="M10 6h4"></path><path d="M10 10h4"></path><path d="M10 14h4"></path><path d="M10 18h4"></path></svg></div>Pattern 1: The Size-Class Divide Persists Despite Overall Growth</h4><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium text-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Across all markets with available data, AI adoption shows pronounced size-class disparity that has not narrowed despite overall market acceleration.</p><div class="mb-8" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h5 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center gap-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-llpa-blue/15 " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.15); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text w-3.5 h-3.5 text-llpa-blue"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg></div>Evidence (December 2025)</h5><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground italic bg-muted/50 p-4 rounded-xl mb-3" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); background-color: rgba(240, 242, 244, 0.5); font-style: italic; font-size: 14px; padding: 16px; padding-top: 16px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 12px;">Note: Gap measured in percentage points (pp).</p><div class="overflow-x-auto" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><table class="w-full text-sm"><thead><tr class="border-b-2 border-foreground"><th class="py-3 font-semibold text-foreground pr-4 text-left " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px 12px 1px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 1px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Market</th><th class="py-3 font-semibold text-foreground px-4 text-left " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Large Enterprise</th><th class="py-3 font-semibold text-foreground px-4 text-left " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Gap</th><th class="py-3 font-semibold text-foreground pl-4 text-left " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 1px 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 1px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">SME/Small</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="border-b border-border "><td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px 12px 1px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 1px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">EU Average</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">41% (250+ employees)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-yellow font-medium" style="color: rgb(249, 184, 31); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">30pp</span></td><td class="py-3 pl-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 1px 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 1px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">11% (10-49 employees)</td></tr><tr class="border-b border-border "><td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px 12px 1px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 1px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Denmark<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Eurostat December 2025: EU enterprise AI adoption reached 20.0%" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[375]</sup></td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">74.5% (250+ employees)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-yellow font-medium" style="color: rgb(249, 184, 31); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">37pp</span></td><td class="py-3 pl-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 1px 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 1px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">37.5% (10-49 employees)</td></tr><tr class="border-b border-border "><td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px 12px 1px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 1px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Finland<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Statsandgraphs: AI adoption in European businesses in 2024" style="c