rder-width: 0px;"><ul class="recharts-default-legend" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;"><li class="recharts-legend-item legend-item-0" style="display: inline-block; margin-right: 10px;color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><svg class="recharts-surface" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 32 32" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 4px;"><title></title><desc></desc><path fill="hsl(var(--llpa-blue))" cx="16" cy="16" class="recharts-symbols" transform="translate(16, 16)" d="M-16,-16h32v32h-32Z"></path></svg><span class="recharts-legend-item-text" style="color: hsl(var(--llpa-blue));color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Large Enterprise</span></li><li class="recharts-legend-item legend-item-1" style="display: inline-block; margin-right: 10px;color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><svg class="recharts-surface" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 32 32" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 4px;"><title></title><desc></desc><path fill="hsl(var(--llpa-orange))" cx="16" cy="16" class="recharts-symbols" transform="translate(16, 16)" d="M-16,-16h32v32h-32Z"></path></svg><span class="recharts-legend-item-text" style="color: hsl(var(--llpa-orange));color: rgb(232, 91, 48); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">SME/Small Business</span></li></ul></div><div tabindex="-1" class="recharts-tooltip-wrapper" style="visibility: hidden; pointer-events: none; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px;color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="mb-8" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h5 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center gap-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-llpa-orange/15 " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(232, 91, 48, 0.15); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-lightbulb w-3.5 h-3.5 text-llpa-orange"><path d="M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5"></path><path d="M9 18h6"></path><path d="M10 22h4"></path></svg></div>Key Finding</h5><div class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p class="mb-3" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">The size-class gap has widened as large enterprises accelerated adoption faster than SMEs. In several markets, large enterprise adoption exceeds 60% while small business adoption remains below 20%.</p><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground border-l-2 border-llpa-yellow/50 pl-3" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; padding-left: 12px; border-top: 0px solid rgba(249, 184, 31, 0.5); border-right: 0px solid rgba(249, 184, 31, 0.5); border-bottom: 0px solid rgba(249, 184, 31, 0.5); border-left: 2px solid rgba(249, 184, 31, 0.5); border-color: rgba(249, 184, 31, 0.5); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 2px;"><strong style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Reading the table — absolute gap vs. ratio:</strong> the "Gap" column is a percentage-point difference, which mechanically shrinks in low-adoption markets. <strong class="text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Romania's 17pp gap is the smallest in the table, but its <em style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 700; font-style: italic; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">large-to-small ratio</em> (5.0x) is the highest</strong> — large Romanian enterprises adopt AI at five times the rate of small ones, more concentrated than the EU average (3.7x), Singapore (4.3x) or the Nordic markets (~4x). The divide is not less severe in Romania; it is hidden by the low floor (small-enterprise adoption of just 4.13%). Read the two columns together when comparing low-base markets to the rest.</p></div></div><div class="mb-8" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h5 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center gap-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-llpa-green/15 " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(104, 198, 57, 0.15); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5 text-llpa-green"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></div>Strategic Recommendations</h5><div class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">See <a href="#demand-pattern-1" class="text-llpa-blue hover:underline font-medium" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Demand Pattern 1 (Section 2)</a> for detailed recommendations addressing this divide.</p></div></div></div><div id="pattern-2" class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6 border border-border shadow-sm mb-10" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; padding: 24px; padding-top: 24px; padding-right: 24px; padding-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 40px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 12px;"><h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center gap-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-llpa-blue/15 " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.15); font-weight: 600; font-size: 20px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-graduation-cap w-4 h-4 text-llpa-blue"><path d="M21.42 10.922a1 1 0 0 0-.019-1.838L12.83 5.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 9.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.832l8.57 3.908a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0z"></path><path d="M22 10v6"></path><path d="M6 12.5V16a6 3 0 0 0 12 0v-3.5"></path></svg></div>Pattern 2: Skills Gap Remains Universal Despite Adoption Growth</h4><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium text-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Counterintuitively, the skills gap has not narrowed as adoption increased. Markets with 30-40% adoption report skills shortages as severe as markets with 10% adoption.</p><div class="mb-8" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h5 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center gap-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-llpa-blue/15 " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.15); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text w-3.5 h-3.5 text-llpa-blue"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg></div>Evidence Across Tiers</h5><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">The skills gap persists across all market tiers.</p><div class="space-y-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground mb-2" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Among Tier 1 leaders:</p><ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground"><li class="flex gap-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-green mt-1.5" style="color: rgb(104, 198, 57); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 6px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Denmark reports 42.03% adoption yet 62% of organizations cite lack of AI skills as a major barrier.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Eurostat December 2025: EU enterprise AI adoption reached 20.0%" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[375]</sup><sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Health &amp; Safety International: Skills gap stops 62% of Danish companies embracing AI" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[26]</sup></span></li><li class="flex gap-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-green mt-1.5" style="color: rgb(104, 198, 57); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 6px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">The Netherlands sees ~25% adoption (above EU average) but a striking 74.6% identify "lack of experience" as their primary obstacle.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="HostingJournalist: Netherlands Sees Surge in AI Integration" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[42]</sup></span></li><li class="flex gap-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-green mt-1.5" style="color: rgb(104, 198, 57); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 6px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Switzerland shows the same pattern among SMEs: the AXA/Sotomo survey of 300 Swiss SMEs finds 55% have started integrating AI (22% fully, 33% experimenting), but integration skews heavily by firm size — 52% of firms with 50+ employees view AI positively vs just 27% of firms with 5–9 employees — signalling adoption has outpaced organizational capability.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="AXA Switzerland / Sotomo SME AI Survey 2024 (via Swiss Federal SME Portal): Swiss SME AI Survey 2024 (AXA / Sotomo Institute, n=300 SMEs) — 55% of Swiss SMEs have started integrating AI; 22% have fully integrated it in at least some projects; 33% are experimenting. Primary use cases: translations (48%), email/letter drafting (40%), ad content (36%). Attitudes and integration vary widely by firm size — 52% of firms with 50+ employees see AI positively vs 27% of firms with 5–9 employees." style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[380]</sup></span></li></ul></div><div style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground mb-2" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">In Tier 2:</p><ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground"><li class="flex gap-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-blue mt-1.5" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 6px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Germany's 20-27% adoption is constrained by skills scarcity, with 33% of organizations citing limited AI talent as their top barrier.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="IBM: Global AI Adoption Index 2023" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[76]</sup></span></li><li class="flex gap-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-blue mt-1.5" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 6px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">South Africa remains early-stage with over 60% identifying the skills gap as their key barrier.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="World Economic Forum: Future of Jobs Report 2025 — skills gap identified as the key barrier to business transformation for a majority of employers" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[390]</sup></span></li><li class="flex gap-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-blue mt-1.5" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 6px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Mexico has reached 95% enterprise AI adoption, but organizational culture and operational complexity — not software availability — are cited as the primary obstacles to scaling, and 100% of Mexican CEOs identify AI investment as the principal lever for profitability and growth.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Bain &amp; Company: AI en México: del entusiasmo a la escala real (95% of Mexican large companies adopting AI; URL may reject automated probes with 403; verified live in browser)" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[521]</sup><sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="EY-Parthenon: CEO Outlook 2026 — Mexico edition: 100% of Mexican CEOs cite AI investment as the primary lever for profitability and growth; 22% report AI results exceeding expectations; 64% plan to maintain or increase AI-specialized talent hiring; 92% anticipate revenue increase from AI. Primary obstacles to scaling AI: operational complexity and organizational culture — not software availability." style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[522]</sup></span></li><li class="flex gap-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-blue mt-1.5" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 6px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Romania — the EU's lowest-adoption market at 5.2% — shows the same skills-gap pattern from a low base: members report low digital literacy and a conservative client mindset, with demand concentrated on awareness and foundational topics rather than advanced AI skills.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Eurostat December 2025: EU enterprise AI adoption reached 20.0%" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[375]</sup><sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Training Provider Survey: Eastern Europe" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[150]</sup></span></li></ul></div><div style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground mb-2" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Tier 3 markets face similar challenges at earlier stages:</p><ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground"><li class="flex gap-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-yellow mt-1.5" style="color: rgb(249, 184, 31); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 6px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Portugal struggles to scale beyond 13-15% adoption with 71% reporting difficulty hiring digital skills.<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Edstellar / AWS: Portugal Skills in Demand Report — 71% of businesses cite difficulty hiring staff with digital skills" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[384]</sup></span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6 border border-border shadow-sm mb-8" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; padding: 24px; padding-top: 24px; padding-right: 24px; padding-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 12px;"><h5 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center gap-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-llpa-yellow/15 " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(249, 184, 31, 0.15); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square w-3.5 h-3.5 text-llpa-yellow"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg></div>Interpretation</h5><div class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">The evidence demonstrates that skills gaps persist regardless of market maturity level — high-adoption markets (Denmark at 42.03%, Netherlands at ~25%) report skill shortages at comparable severity to early-stage markets (South Africa, Portugal). This pattern suggests the skills gap is <strong style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">structural rather than a temporary lag</strong> that resolves with increased adoption. As organizations progress through adoption stages, they encounter new skill requirements rather than "catching up."</p></div></div><div class="mb-8" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h5 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center gap-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-llpa-green/15 " style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgba(104, 198, 57, 0.15); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3.5 h-3.5 text-llpa-green"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></div>Strategic Recommendations: Learning Pathway Levels</h5><div class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p class="mb-4" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Develop leveled learning pathways</strong> spanning the full organizational-maturity spectrum — from strategic transformation work for AI-native enterprises down to foundational literacy for early adopters.</p><p class="mb-6 text-sm text-muted-foreground border-l-2 border-llpa-blue/40 pl-3" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 12px; padding-left: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px; border-top: 0px solid rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.4); border-right: 0px solid rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.4); border-bottom: 0px solid rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.4); border-left: 2px solid rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.4); border-color: rgba(32, 159, 223, 0.4); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 2px;"><strong style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Note:</strong> the level numbering aligns with Section 1.1's Market Maturity Tiers — Level 1 is for the most advanced organizations, Level 4 for those just starting. The two systems are still independent: tiers describe whole markets; levels describe individual organizations' learning needs.</p><div class="space-y-3" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="rounded-xl p-4 border-l-4 border-l-llpa-orange bg-llpa-orange/10" style=" color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; padding: 16px; padding-top: 16px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 16px; border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 4px solid rgb(232, 91, 48); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235) rgb(224, 230, 235) rgb(224, 230, 235) rgb(232, 91, 48); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 4px; border-radius: 12px;"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="w-6 h-6 rounded flex items-center justify-center bg-llpa-orange/20" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 4px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-brain w-3 h-3 text-llpa-orange"><path d="M12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.997.125 4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77 4 4 0 0 0 .556 6.588A4 4 0 1 0 12 18Z"></path><path d="M12 5a3 3 0 1 1 5.997.125 4 4 0 0 1 2.526 5.77 4 4 0 0 1-.556 6.588A4 4 0 1 1 12 18Z"></path><path d="M15 13a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-3-4 4.5 4.5 0 0 1-3 4"></path><path d="M17.599 6.5a3 3 0 0 0 .399-1.375"></path><path d="M6.003 5.125A3 3 0 0 0 6.401 6.5"></path><path d="M3.477 10.896a4 4 0 0 1 .585-.396"></path><path d="M19.938 10.5a4 4 0 0 1 .585.396"></path><path d="M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-1.967-.516"></path><path d="M19.967 17.484A4 4 0 0 1 18 18"></path></svg></div><span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-llpa-orange" style="color: rgb(232, 91, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Level 1</span><h6 class="text-base font-semibold text-foreground" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Strategic AI Transformation</h6></div><p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 italic" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-style: italic; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 700; font-style: italic; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Target:</strong> Organizations where AI is embedded across most business functions; multiple production AI systems generating measurable business value; dedicated AI/ML teams</p><div style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground mb-1" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 4px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Learning Objectives:</p><ul class="space-y-1"><li class="text-xs text-muted-foreground flex gap-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="flex-shrink-0 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-1.5 bg-llpa-orange" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 6px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 9999px;"></span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 2