rder: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">88% of organizations using AI, but only 39% report any EBIT impact at enterprise level; nearly two-thirds still in experimentation/pilot phase; only 6% are "high performers" capturing significant value<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="McKinsey State of AI: 88% using AI, only 6% high performers" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[393]</sup></span></li><li class="text-muted-foreground flex items-start gap-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-blue mt-1" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 4px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">82% of leaders say this is a pivotal year to rethink strategy, yet 67% of leaders report familiarity with AI agents compared to only 40% of employees — highlighting the execution gap<sup class="citation-link text-xs ml-0.5 cursor-pointer" title="Microsoft: Work Trend Index 2025 — 82% of leaders say this is a pivotal year to rethink strategy; 67% of leaders are familiar or extremely familiar with AI agents vs just 40% of employees" style="color: rgb(32, 159, 223); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">[394]</sup></span></li><li class="text-muted-foreground flex items-start gap-2" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-llpa-yellow mt-1" style="color: rgb(249, 184, 31); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 4px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-l