nt processing</li></ul></div><div style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground mb-1" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 4px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Key Barriers</p><ul class="text-sm text-foreground/80 space-y-1"><li class="flex items-start gap-2" style="color: rgba(29, 38, 48, 0.8); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-destructive" style="color: rgb(239, 67, 67); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span>Procurement complexity</li><li class="flex items-start gap-2" style="color: rgba(29, 38, 48, 0.8); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-destructive" style="color: rgb(239, 67, 67); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">•</span>Transparency requirements</li></ul></div><div class="pt-2 border-t border-border" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; padding: 8px 0px 0px; padding-top: 8px; margin-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px 0px 0px;"><p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground italic" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-style: italic; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Growing adoption driven by efficiency mandates; governance requirements creating structured approaches</p></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-12" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 48px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-6" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Cross-Industry Insights</h3><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="undefined p-6 border-l-4 border-llpa-blue" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; padding: 24px; padding-top: 24px; padding-right: 24px; padding-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 24px; border-top: 0px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-right: 0px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-left: 4px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-color: rgb(32, 159, 223); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 4px;"><h4 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Regulated Industries Lead in Governance</h4><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Financial services, healthcare, and public sector show more mature AI governance frameworks, driven by regulatory requirements. This structured approach correlates with higher value realization rates.</p></div><div class="undefined p-6 border-l-4 border-llpa-blue" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; padding: 24px; padding-top: 24px; padding-right: 24px; padding-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 24px; border-top: 0px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-right: 0px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-left: 4px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-color: rgb(32, 159, 223); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 4px;"><h4 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Skills Gap Persists Across All Sectors</h4><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Despite varying adoption rates, all industries report skills gaps as a top-3 barrier. Technical skills (data science, ML engineering) and strategic skills (AI strategy, change management) both in short supply.</p></div><div class="undefined p-6 border-l-4 border-llpa-blue" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; padding: 24px; padding-top: 24px; padding-right: 24px; padding-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 24px; border-top: 0px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-right: 0px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-left: 4px solid rgb(32, 159, 223); border-color: rgb(32, 159, 223); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 4px;"><h4 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Customer-Facing AI Most Mature</h4><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Chatbots, recommendation engines, and personalization have highest deployment rates. Back-office and operational AI adoption growing but less mature.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id="productivity-analysis" class="py-24 bg-background" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; padding: 96px 0px; padding-top: 96px; padding-bottom: 96px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="container" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; padding: 0px 32px; padding-right: 32px; padding-left: 32px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="mb-10" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 40px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p class="font-body text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Section 4</p><h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">The Productivity Evidence Gap</h2><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-4" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">A central question in AI adoption research is whether documented productivity gains translate to aggregate economic impact. Current evidence reveals a significant gap between micro-level findings and macro-level statistics — a pattern with important implications for interpreting claims that "AI hype is dying."</p></div><div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-lg p-6 mb-10" style=" color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; padding: 24px; padding-top: 24px; padding-right: 24px; padding-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 40px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-lg mb-3" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Research Summary</h3><p class="text-white/90 mb-4" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">The narrative that AI hype is dying is understandable given current evidence — enterprises bought AI tools and aren't seeing returns; productivity gains aren't showing up in labor market data. However, this interpretation conflates <strong style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">a temporary plateau in one phase of adoption</strong> with evidence of fundamental technology limitations.</p><p class="text-white/80 text-sm" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">This section presents the evidence for both the productivity gap and the argument that it represents a phase transition rather than a ceiling on AI capability.</p></div><div id="productivity-evidence" class="mb-12" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">4.1 Task-Level Productivity Gains (Micro Evidence)</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground mb-6" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Controlled studies consistently document significant productivity improvements at the task level.</p><div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-6" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><table class="w-full text-sm"><thead><tr class="bg-muted border-b"><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Study</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Sample</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Finding</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">NBER Executive Survey (2025)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground align-top" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">6,000 executives</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">90% of firms report zero measurable productivity or employment impact despite $2.5 trillion global AI spending</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">GitHub Copilot Study (Peng et al. 2023)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground align-top" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Software developers</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">55% faster task completion for coding tasks</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Customer Service Study (Brynjolfsson et al. 2025)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground align-top" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">5,179 customer service agents</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">14% increase in issues resolved per hour; novice workers improved 34%, top performers showed minimal gains</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">BCG Consulting Study (Dell'Acqua et al. 2023)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground align-top" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">758 consultants</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">25% faster completion, 40% higher quality for AI-suitable tasks; 19% worse performance on tasks requiring judgment</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">METR Study (2025)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground align-top" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Experienced open-source developers</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">19% longer to complete real coding tasks with AI tools, though perceived themselves as 20% faster</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">CEO Survey (BuildMVPFast 2025)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground align-top" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Enterprise CEOs</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">95% of companies report zero measurable productivity ROI; 95% of AI pilots never escape the lab</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgb(255, 251, 235); font-size: 16px; padding: 16px; padding-top: 16px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 16px; border: 1px solid rgb(253, 230, 138); border-top: 1px solid rgb(253, 230, 138); border-right: 1px solid rgb(253, 230, 138); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(253, 230, 138); border-left: 1px solid rgb(253, 230, 138); border-color: rgb(253, 230, 138); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><p class="text-sm text-amber-900" style="color: rgb(120, 53, 15); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(120, 53, 15); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Key Pattern:</strong> Gains are real but context-dependent. Novice workers improve disproportionately (34% vs minimal for experts). Experienced developers may actually take longer while perceiving themselves as faster. AI accelerates drafting but creates downstream verification work — what researchers call "workslop."</p></div></div><div id="macro-evidence" class="mb-12" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">4.2 Aggregate Economic Impact (Macro Evidence)</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground mb-6" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Despite task-level gains, aggregate statistics show minimal measurable impact.</p><div class="space-y-4 mb-6" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="border rounded-lg p-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; padding: 16px; padding-top: 16px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 16px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">BLS Productivity Data (2025-2025)</h4><p class="text-sm text-foreground mb-2" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">US productivity growth: 2.7% in 2025 vs 1.4% decade average — early signs of acceleration</p><p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground italic" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-style: italic; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Suggestive but not conclusive; confounded by other economic factors</p></div><div class="border rounded-lg p-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; padding: 16px; padding-top: 16px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 16px; margin-top: 16px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Eurostat Enterprise Survey (2025)</h4><p class="text-sm text-foreground mb-2" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Enterprise AI adoption reached 20% EU average, up from 8% in 2023</p><p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground italic" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-style: italic; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Adoption metrics improving but not yet reflected in aggregate output statistics</p></div><div class="border rounded-lg p-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; padding: 16px; padding-top: 16px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 16px; margin-top: 16px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">UK Office for National Statistics (2025)</h4><p class="text-sm text-foreground mb-2" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Most businesses report no measurable productivity impact from AI adoption</p><p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground italic" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-style: italic; font-size: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Consistent with deployment-value gap pattern observed across markets</p></div></div><div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; padding: 16px; padding-top: 16px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 16px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">The Central Paradox:</strong> Task-level studies document 14-55% productivity gains. Aggregate data shows 90-95% of firms reporting zero measurable impact. This disconnect defines the current phase of AI adoption.</p></div></div><div id="micro-macro-gap" class="mb-12" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">4.3 Historical Precedent: The Solow Paradox</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground mb-6" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">In 1987, economist Robert Solow observed: "You can see the computer age everywhere but in the productivity statistics." The current AI pattern mirrors this historical precedent.</p><div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-6" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><table class="w-full text-sm"><thead><tr class="bg-muted border-b"><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold w-1/4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Dimension</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Computing (1980s)</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">AI (2020s)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Investment vs. Returns</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Hundredfold increase in computing capacity; productivity growth dropped from 3% to 1%</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">$2.5 trillion global AI spending; 95% of firms report no measurable productivity impact</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Time to Impact</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">10-15 years (1980-1995) before IT productivity gains appeared in macro data</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Unknown; economists debate whether J-curve arrives 2027 or 2037</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Resolution Pattern</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Gains emerged when organizations redesigned processes around technology (Walmart supply chain, financial services)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Early evidence suggests same pattern: 95% bolted AI onto existing workflows rather than redesigning around it</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-lg p-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgb(236, 253, 245); font-size: 16px; padding: 16px; padding-top: 16px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 16px; border: 1px solid rgb(167, 243, 208); border-top: 1px solid rgb(167, 243, 208); border-right: 1px solid rgb(167, 243, 208); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(167, 243, 208); border-left: 1px solid rgb(167, 243, 208); border-color: rgb(167, 243, 208); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><p class="text-sm text-emerald-900" style="color: rgb(6, 78, 59); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(6, 78, 59); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Resolution Pattern:</strong> IT productivity gains emerged in the 1990s when organizations redesigned processes around technology rather than bolting computers onto existing workflows. Research suggests the same pattern will determine AI value realization.</p></div></div><div class="mb-12" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">4.4 Why AI Differs from Metaverse/VR Hype Cycles</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground mb-6" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">A critical question is whether current AI adoption patterns reflect the metaverse/VR cycle (hype without sustained capability progress) or the computing cycle (temporary lag before transformative impact).</p><div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-6" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><table class="w-full text-sm"><thead><tr class="bg-muted border-b"><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold w-1/4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Dimension</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">AI (2024-2025)</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Metaverse/VR</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Current Deployment</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">88% enterprise adoption; measurable task-level productivity gains documented</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Limited enterprise adoption; use cases remain primarily consumer entertainment</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Capability Progress</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Benchmarks improving continuously: GPQA Diamond scores rose from 79.2% to 87.3% in months; inference costs dropped 280-fold over two years</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Hardware improvements incremental; fundamental interaction paradigm unchanged since 2016</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Economic Integration</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">GitHub Copilot, ChatGPT, enterprise LLMs embedded in daily workflows of millions</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Virtual offices, metaverse platforms largely abandoned or pivoted by major tech companies</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Investment Trajectory</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Continued scaling: Microsoft $80B, Google $75B, Amazon $100B committed to AI infrastructure 2025-2027</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Meta pivoted from metaverse focus; VR investment declining across major platforms</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgb(239, 246, 255); font-size: 16px; padding: 16px; padding-top: 16px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 16px; border: 1px solid rgb(191, 219, 254); border-top: 1px solid rgb(191, 219, 254); border-right: 1px solid rgb(191, 219, 254); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(191, 219, 254); border-left: 1px solid rgb(191, 219, 254); border-color: rgb(191, 219, 254); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><p class="text-sm text-blue-900" style="color: rgb(30, 58, 138); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(30, 58, 138); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Key Distinction:</strong> AI capabilities continue improving on fundamental metrics (benchmark scores, inference costs, context windows). Metaverse/VR hype collapsed without sustained capability breakthroughs. AI has crossed from theoretical capability to operational implementation embedded in daily workflows of millions.</p></div></div><div class="mb-12" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">4.5 AGI Timeline Forecasts</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground mb-6" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Aggregated forecasts from prediction markets and expert surveys provide context on expected capability trajectories.</p><div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-6" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><table class="w-full text-sm"><thead><tr class="bg-muted border-b"><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Source</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Prediction</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Notes</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Metaculus (Community Forecast)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">First general AI announced: May 2033 (median)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground text-xs" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 12px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Weakly general AI forecast: March 2028</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">AI Impacts ESPAI Survey</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">HLMI (50% probability): 2031-2047 depending on methodology</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground text-xs" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 12px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Timelines shortened by 13 years between 2022-2023 surveys</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium align-top" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">80,000 Hours Analysis (2025)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Expert forecasts contracted from 50 years to 5 years over past four years</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground text-xs" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 12px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">AI company leaders claim AGI within 2-5 years</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="bg-rose-50 border border-rose-200 rounded-lg p-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgb(255, 241, 242); font-size: 16px; padding: 16px; padding-top: 16px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 16px; border: 1px solid rgb(254, 205, 211); border-top: 1px solid rgb(254, 205, 211); border-right: 1px solid rgb(254, 205, 211); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(254, 205, 211); border-left: 1px solid rgb(254, 205, 211); border-color: rgb(254, 205, 211); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><p class="text-sm text-rose-900" style="color: rgb(136, 19, 55); font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(136, 19, 55); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Timeline Implications:</strong> Expert forecasts have contracted dramatically — from 50 years to 5 years over four years. While prediction uncertainty is high, the direction of revision (consistently earlier) suggests current deployment challenges reflect early-phase adoption rather than fundamental capability limits.</p></div></div><div style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">4.6 Interpreting the Evidence</h3><div class="space-y-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">The evidence supports several conclusions:</p><ul class="space-y-3 text-muted-foreground"><li class="flex gap-3" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-foreground font-medium" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">1.</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">The productivity gap is real.</strong> 90-95% of firms report no measurable AI productivity impact despite significant investment.</span></li><li class="flex gap-3" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-foreground font-medium" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">2.</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Task-level gains are also real.</strong> Controlled studies consistently document 14-55% improvements for specific tasks.</span></li><li class="flex gap-3" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-foreground font-medium" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">3.</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">This pattern has historical precedent.</strong> The Solow Paradox showed a 10-15 year lag between IT investment and productivity gains.</span></li><li class="flex gap-3" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-foreground font-medium" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">4.</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">AI differs from previous hype cycles.</strong> Unlike metaverse/VR, AI capabilities continue improving on fundamental metrics and are embedded in daily workflows.</span></li><li class="flex gap-3" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><span class="text-foreground font-medium" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">5. </span><span style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Timeline forecasts suggest limited runway.</strong> AGI predictions have compressed from decades to years, though uncertainty remains high.</span></li></ul><div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-lg p-6 mt-6" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; padding: 24px; padding-top: 24px; padding-right: 24px; padding-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 24px; margin-top: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 8px;"><p class="text-white/90" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><strong style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Bottom Line:</strong> Current evidence is consistent with a temporary plateau between adoption phases rather than evidence that AI has reached its limits. Organizations interpreting current deployment challenges as confirmation that "the hype is dying" may be making the same error as those who dismissed computing's transformative potential in the 1980s.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="future-outlook" class="py-24 bg-background" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; padding: 96px 0px; padding-top: 96px; padding-bottom: 96px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="container" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; padding: 0px 32px; padding-right: 32px; padding-left: 32px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><div class="mb-10" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 40px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><p class="font-body text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Section 5</p><h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Future Outlook</h2><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-4" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">The productivity gap documented in Section 4 reflects a phase transition, not a technology ceiling. This section presents evidence on capability trajectories, AGI timelines, and organizational preparation requirements.</p></div><div class="mb-10" style=" color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 40px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;"><h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">5.1 Evidence of Continued Capability Progress</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground mb-6" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Unlike previous technology hype cycles, AI capabilities continue improving on fundamental performance metrics. This distinguishes current adoption challenges from evidence of technology limits.</p><div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-6" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 1px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px;"><table class="w-full text-sm"><thead><tr class="bg-muted border-b"><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Benchmark</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">2024 Baseline</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">2025</th><th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Change</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">GPQA Diamond (PhD-level reasoning)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">~65%</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">87.3% (Claude 5)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium text-emerald-700" style="color: rgb(4, 120, 87); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">+22 points</td></tr><tr class="border-b last:border-b-0"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 16px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">SWE-bench Verified (real GitHub issues)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-muted-foreground" style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 16px; padding-top: 12px; padding-right: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left