XA Switzerland / Sotomo SME AI Survey 2024 (via Swiss Federal SME Portal)" style="color: rgb(29, 38, 48); font-weight: 500; font-size: 11px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">AXA Switzerland / Sotomo SME AI Survey 2024 (via Swiss Federal SME Portal)</p><p class="font-body text-[10px] text-muted-foreground truncate" title="Swiss SME AI Survey 2024 (AXA / Sotomo Institute, n=300 SMEs) — 55% of Swiss SMEs have started integrating AI; 22% have fully integrated it in at least some projects; 33% are experimenting. Primary use cases: translations (48%), email/letter drafting (40%), ad content (36%). Attitudes and integration vary widely by firm size — 52% of firms with 50+ employees see AI positively vs 27% of firms with 5–9 employees." style="color: rgb(103, 115, 126); font-size: 10px; border: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-top: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-right: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-left: 0px solid rgb(224, 230, 235); border-color: rgb(224, 230, 235); border-style: solid; border-width: 0px;">Swiss SME AI Survey 2024 (AXA / Sotomo Institute, n=300 SMEs) — 55% of Swiss SMEs have started integrating AI; 22% have fully integrated it in at least some projects; 33% are experimenting. Primary use cases: translations (48%), email/letter drafting (40%), ad content (36%). Attitudes and integration vary widely by firm size — 52% of firms with 50+ employees see AI positively vs 27% of firms with 5–9 employees.</p></div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-3 w-3 text-muted-foreground 